Title: Relates to monies included in the environmental protection fund
Summary: Relates to monies included in the environmental protection fund; makes a technical amendment by removing monies collected pursuant to title thirty-three of article fifteen of the environmental conservation law from the monies included in the environmental protection fund.

ActClause: AN ACT to amend the state finance law, in relation to monies included in the environmental protection fund
